{"tid":668802,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩西斯 揚言要捧足總盃 向車路士贖罪","createTime":"2018-05-18T02:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T05:28:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb03518d6b2e48fff2b07f5ee2ad85c31633da8a","tid":668802,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/6/016/21437039016/21445690903_600x389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F6%2F016%2F21437039016%2F21445690903_600x389.jpg&h=f7baf8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=4RKMSrBp3%2BDoZuM3FwVM1kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=238c3e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】今季足總盃決賽在周六上演，車路士翼衛域陀摩西斯希望抹走上季領紅牌兼失盃的不快。<br />\n<br />\n「這事仍在我腦海中，但已發生了，我不能改變它。這肯定是我職業生涯最差的感覺，我希望留在場上幫助隊友。」域陀摩西斯（Victor Moses）於上季足總盃決賽被逐，最終英超盟主車路士以1:2不敵阿仙奴，未能成為國內雙冠王。<br />\n<br />\n車路士今季演出不穩，在英超拿下4連勝後本來有機會殺入前4，可是最後2場只得1和1負，最終僅得第5位，錯失來季歐聯席位，因此足總盃冠軍可說是他們最後的安慰獎。<br />\n<br />\n域陀摩西斯表示：「隊中每位球員都要非常專注，踢出領隊要求我們在場上要做的事，爭取勝利。面對曼聯永遠都是難應付的，他們有具質素的球員，但我們也有，最重要是保持高度集中，確保拿下冠軍。」"},{"pid":"bc47110d55f608abb9bc712e4e91e68c562bc32c","tid":668802,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:09:44.000Z","msg":"講得好！"},{"pid":"3faccacb0eb988adb306636cf63426d37e42ea58","tid":668802,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"5a031cd0429476afdaa5e7a15a4b691226eb4771","tid":668802,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3faccacb0eb988adb306636cf63426d37e42ea58","tid":668802,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"好！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"d53c1bba52f5d5930f26d938010f5b8393560e97","tid":668802,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c7b2497bfb28ad397daa4ca412cce17ceefae1","tid":668802,"uid":1977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"自殺啦垃圾"},{"pid":"e2ad566ce1abeee99b847613676929854ea83afc","tid":668802,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"好波，希望你可以正選落場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18eeaeffe103d7e186298fd8e03f87363cadf291","tid":668802,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ziLTGRM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FziLTGRM.gif&h=2dbf216a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91b8b124eec93166a7d3c8723c7cbf870c454685","tid":668802,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"18eeaeffe103d7e186298fd8e03f87363cadf291","tid":668802,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ziLTGRM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FziLTGRM.gif&h=2dbf216a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:28:14.000Z","msg":"皇馬已經判左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}